    "name": "Tinderbox\n* This small container holds flint, fire steel, an tinder (usually dry cloth soaked in light oil) used to kindle a fire. Using it to light a torch — or anything else with abundant, exposed fuel — takes an action. Lighting any other fire takes 1 minutes.",
